frameDefinitions: These words refer to separating a Whole into Parts, or separating one part from another.
A Whole separates into Parts, or one part of a whole, called Part_1, becomes separate from the remaining portion, Part_2.
These words relate to the relative ordering of two events or times.
An Agent suddenly and often violently separates the Whole_patient into two or more smaller Pieces, resulting in the Whole_patient no longer existing as such.
An Agent causes a Firearm to discharge which induces the rapid motion of the Projectile.
